  "note": "The ONLY classification system used by canonical-project-model. Every trade, line item, cost code, submittal, quick link, critical-path item, and scope record is assigned a two-digit MasterFormat division; the division number is the universal sort key for documents, pages, tables, and every workbook sheet. Divisions 01-32 are the primary working range for commercial construction and JOC; 00 and 33-48 are included so coding/sorting never fails on an out-of-range division.",
